Local mode (default)
  dwiforge.sh → subject loop → stage functions inline

SLURM submitter mode (--slurm)
  dwiforge.sh → generates and submits job array
              → each array task runs dwiforge.sh --slurm-worker $sub
              → worker runs the same stage scripts, same config

SLURM worker mode (--slurm-worker sub-001)
  Single subject, all stages, no loop
  Reads config from TOML, exports paths, runs stages sequentially